import { Box, Heading, HStack } from '@chakra-ui/core'
import { MdMovie } from 'react-icons/md'

export default function Movie () {
  return <Box maxW={1200} mx="auto" mt="20px">
    <HStack fontSize="24px">
      <MdMovie />
      <Heading as="h3" fontSize="24px">电影</Heading>
    </HStack>
    <HStack>
      <Box>
        <Image src="/images/item_1.jpg" />
        <Text>Marvel Mission Recap: Captain Marvel's Star of Hala</Text>
      </Box>
    </HStack>
  </Box>
}
